Other programs to look out for...


Ponga - Pong tennis clone by me (bit crap actually but quite fun!).

ScaleConv - A scale converter written in pascal.  Converts all measurements
             of a the same type to othe scales. (time - seconds -> minutes).
            Covers time, distance (metres furlongs, Nautical Miles, hands, etc),
             speed (mph, kph, knots, etc.), I'm sure you get the idea.
            (By me)

ClockWobble - You set an alarm and the screen wobbles a bit. (Crap really)
               (By me)

F1GP-ED - Wonderful editor for MicroProse F1GP, by Oliver Roberts.
          Get it, it's brilliant...then register it and it's even more fun!


